{
  "stem": "3848.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I went to school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And when I was five years old, I started to go to Cheder to learn Yiddish and Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When I was seven years old, I started a public school, the Polish public school, which was compulsory at that time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And when I finished public school, I signed into a special school, [INAUDIBLE] sponsored by American [INAUDIBLE] until the beginning of the war of 1939, when--",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was interrupted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was, at the time of the war, 17 years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And in 1939, when [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the war started with Poland, like Germany and Poland, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Russia made a pact, or agreement, with Germany to divide Poland in half.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When the Germans took Poland up to the River Bug, near Lvov and Kovel and Brest-Litovsk, around that area.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Russians came in on the other side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they took the part where I lived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So automatically, when the Russians came into us in September of 1939, I was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] already on the Russian camp, sort of saying.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I started to go to Russian schools.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was that mandatory?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wanted to learned the Russian language.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Although in my young age, I spoke Ukrainian, because I used to play with Ukrainian friends.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And so it was easier for me to learn the language of Russian because it's similar.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was anti-Semitism at all times in Poland and in my area.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were sort of used to that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We accepted it because we felt that we don't live in our own country.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had a lot of problems.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
